reviews.name: LD Compatible Replacement for Samsung MLT-D105L Black HY Laser Toner Cartridge for use in Samsung ML, SCX, & SF Printers
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for this cartridge every where could not believe what they were trying to charge, then I found LD Company. I ordered this and so happy I did. I ordered it on 7/21 in the pm, they said it would arrive on 7/31 well to my surprise it arrived 7/23 am ,2-days wow so happy as I have college kids that print all the time. The print is great, product easy to install, no wasteful packaging-5 stars all the way !!! Samsung scx-4623F
reviews.title: Product is GREAT
